 Soi Samerjai", "notes": "Khao Soi只要約50泰銖！中午常排隊，建議11點前到。只有泰文菜單，但只點Khao Soi就對了。", "phone": null, "awards": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/thailand/7091cd3e-dde1-43bc-b166-9ce19c39e37d-1.jpeg"], "rating": null, "address": null, "city_id": "chiang-mai", "ratings": null, "website": null, "category": "餐廳 / Restaurant", "currency": "TWD", "latitude": 18.7889, "chef_name": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": 98.9992, "meal_type": null, "region_id": null, "address_en": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2026-04-06T23:23:06.268673+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "dress_code": null, "facilities": null, "green_star": false, "highlights": null, "name_local": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "best_season": null, "description": "《Khao Soi Samerjai》這碗咖哩麵，老闆娘煮了四十年。湯頭的椰奶不會蓋過香料，酥脆麵條在湯裡慢慢軟化，剛好是第三口開始最好吃的狀態。泰北咖哩的層次在這裡被精準掌握：薑黃的土壤氣味、椰奶的甜潤、辣椒的後勁，三者平衡得恰到好處。牆上泛黃的菜單、磨損的木桌、老闆娘熟練但不敷衍的動作——這些都是時間累積的證明。不是網紅店，是生活的一部分。清邁在地人從小吃到大的味道，比任何米其林推薦都更真實。", "is_featured": false, "menu_images": null, "price_range": null, "specialties": null, "bib_gourmand": false, "chef_profile": null, "country_code": "TH", "cuisine_type": null, "dining_style": null, "english_name": "Khao Soi Samerjai", "private_room": false, "review_count": 0, "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_notes": null, "booking_phone": null, "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "description_en": null, "group_friendly": true, "internal_notes": null, "max_group_size": null, "michelin_plate": false, "michelin_stars": null, "min_group_size": null, "avg_price_lunch": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "dietary_options": null, "google_maps_url": null, "recommended_for": null, "reservation_url": null, "avg_price_dinner": null, "group_menu_price": null, "signature_dishes": null, "