: false, "highlights": null, "name_local": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "best_season": null, "description": "仁川中華街，韓國最大的中華街，位於仁川站附近。19世紀清朝移民在此聚集，保留中式建築、牌樓、關帝廟。炸醬麵是這裡的招牌美食，共和春本店是元祖。街道兩旁有中式餐廳、雜貨店、旅行社。這是認識韓國華僑歷史的好地方，也是品嚐韓式炸醬麵的最佳場所。適合半日遊，可搭配仁川開港場、童話村一起遊覽。", "is_featured": false, "menu_images": null, "price_range": null, "specialties": null, "bib_gourmand": false, "chef_profile": null, "country_code": "KR", "cuisine_type": null, "dining_style": null, "english_name": "Incheon Chinatown", "private_room": false, "review_count": 0, "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_notes": null, "booking_phone": null, "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "description_en": null, "group_friendly": true, "internal_notes": null, "max_group_size": null, "michelin_plate": false, "michelin_stars": null, "min_group_size": null, "avg_price_lunch": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "dietary_options": null, "google_maps_url": null, "recommended_for": null, "reservation_url": null, "avg_price_dinner": null, "group_menu_price": null, "signature_dishes": null, "group_menu_options": null, "dining_restrictions": null, "michelin_guide_year": null, "group_menu_available": false, "reservation_required": false, "private_room_capacity": null}, {"id": "372d970f-703a-4723-9d35-51ba662d0c6e", "fax": null, "name": "石垣牛燒肉", "notes": "沖繩石垣島特產的頂級和牛，脂肪分布均勻入口即化。在地燒肉店可品嚐新鮮直送的各部位，是沖繩必吃美食。", "phone": null, "awards": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/1f900ef5-5dc7-4cb0-ac82-b471ac02b34d-1.jpeg"], "rating": null, "address": null, "city_id": "ishigaki", "ratings": null, "website": null, "category": "餐廳 / Restaurant", "currency": "TWD", "latitude": 24.3448, "chef_name": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": 124.1557, "meal_type": null, "region_id": "jp_okinawa", "address_en": null, "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-04-06T23:24:29.035585+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "dress_code": null, "facilities": null, "green_star": false, "highlights": null, "name_local": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "best_season": null, "description": "石垣牛燒肉，石垣島品牌和牛，肉質細嫩、油花均勻、入口即化。燒肉、牛排、牛丼、握壽司都很美味。やまもと、ひとし石敢當店、金城都是名店。這是石垣島必吃美食，也是日本頂級和牛之一。價格約4,000-10,000日圓/人。可搭配石垣泡盛、海葡萄一起品嚐。需提前預訂熱門店家。", "is_featured": false, "menu_images": null, "price_range": null, "specialties": null, "bib_gourmand": false, "chef_profile": null, "country_code": "JP", "cuisine_type": null, "dining_style": null, "english_name": null, "private_room": false, "review_count": 0, "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_notes": null, "booking_phone": null, "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "description_en": null, "group_friendly": true, "internal_notes": null, "max_group_size": null, "michelin_plate": false, "michelin_stars": null, "min_group_size": null, "avg_price_lunch": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "dietary_options": null, "google_maps_url": null, "recommended_for": null, "reservation_url": null, "avg_price_dinner": null, "group_menu_price": null, "signature_dishes": null, "group_menu_options": null, "dining_restrictions": null, "michelin_guide_year": null, "group_menu_available": false, "reservation_required": false, "private_room_capacity": null}, {"id": "377ab9a9-bbad-42da-b17f-ad1ba238138f", "fax": null, "name": "瓢亭", "notes": "創業 400 年的京都老舖，瓢亭玉子是傳奇朝粥的靈魂，被譽為早餐界的米其林。", "phone": null, "awards": null, "images": ["https://pfqvdacxowpgfamuvnsn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/attractions/japan/a63b742f-b637-49e4-843e-c8dab595620d-1.jpeg"], "rating": null, "address": null, "city_id": "kyoto", "ratings": null, "website": null, "category": "餐廳 / Restaurant", "currency": "TWD", "latitude": 35.0112, "chef_name": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": 135.7847, "meal_type": null, "region_id": "jp_kansai", "address_en": null, "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-04-06T23:22:38.552842+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "dress_code": null, "facilities": null, "green_star": false, "highlights": null, "name_local": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "best_season": null, "description": "京都南禪寺旁的米其林三星懷石料理店，創業超過400年，是京都料理最高峰。招牌「瓢亭玉子」滑嫩鮮美，朝粥套餐清雅精緻。午餐相對親民，晚餐需預約且價格昂貴。庭園四季景致優美，用餐彷彿時空凍結。是體驗京都料理極致美學與百年老舖傳統的夢幻餐廳。", "is_featured": false, "menu_images": null, "price_range": null, "specialties": null, "bib_gourmand": false, "chef_profile": null, "country_code": "JP", "cuisine_type": null, "dining_style": null, "english_name": "Hyotei", "private_room": false, "review_count": 0, "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_notes": null, "booking_phone": null, "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "opening_hours": null, "deleted_reason": null, "description_en": null, "group_friendly": true, "internal_notes": null, "max_group_size": null, "michelin_plate": false, "michelin_stars": null, "min_group_size": null, "avg_price_lunch": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "dietary_options": null, "google_maps_url": null, "recommended_for": null, "reservation_url": null, "avg_price_dinner": null, "group_menu_price": null, "signature_dishes": null, "group_menu_options": null, "dining_restrictions": null, "michelin_guide_year": null, "group_menu_available": false, "reservation_required": false, "private_room_capacity": null}, {"id": "37af2260-f572-4d9d-9914-9cf6d9cfb6bb", "fax": null, "name": "Rico's Lechon", "notes": "宿霧的烤乳豬名店，與Zubuchon齊名。多年傳統配方，是當地人推薦的美食。", "phone": null, "awards": null, "images": null, "rating": null, "address": null, "city_id": "bohol", "ratings": null, "website": null, "category": "餐廳 / Restaurant", "currency": "TWD", "la